latestIgtvVideos.title: How to use Aloe Vera ✨🌱
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
1. Using it for face :-
INGREDIENTS (face pack)
* aloes vera gel 🌱
* Rose water 🌹
* Honey 🍯 
* Turmeric 
* Lemon 🍋 

2. Using it for hair:-
* Apply directly after cutting 
* Or apply gelly on your hair
These two remedies are totally effective and working ! Must try 💕
.

1 - Aloe vera is a best cleanser , remove tan / sun burn , moisture your skin and remove Acne too. It has anti aging properties, cooling properties , removes dead skin.
 
2 - Turmeric helps to brighten your skin , it has anti bacterial properties so it removes pimples
 too. 

3 -honey is a best cleanser make your skin glowing and brighten.

4 -Lemon haa Vitamin C which helps to remove dead cells and clean pours deeply !!

5 -Rose water has antibacterial properties , Antioxidants , Moistures your skin, Astringent properties.
